dragon crown group holdings (935) Details


			Dragon Crown Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides integrated terminal services for liquid chemical products in the People’s Republic of China. It specializes in the storage and handling of liquid chemical products, including loading and discharging of liquid chemical products at its jetties; storage of liquid chemical products at its tank farm; and delivery of such products through its pipelines and other basic terminal infrastructure. The company operates two terminals located in Nanjing and Ningbo. It is also involved in the provision of marketing services; finance and management services; accounting services; administrative and technical services; and business development services. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong. Dragon Crown Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Lirun Limited.
  			

