                                                Dragon Crown Group Holdings Limited
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Dragon Crown Group Holdings Limited operates in the General warehousing and storage sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Dragon Crown Group Holdings Limited with three other
	trucking and warehousing companies in Asia:
		
	Beijing Properties (Holdings) Ltd
	
		of Hong Kong
		(2016
	sales of 317.97 million Hong Kong Dollars [US$40.71  million]
		of which 56%
		was Logistics Business),
	
	Zhuhai Winbase International Chemical Tank Terminal Company Limited
	
		(209.14 million Chinese Renmimbi [US$31.09  million]
		of which 50%
		was Handling), and
	
	Snowman Logistics Ltd
	
		which is
		
		based in India
		(2.40 billion Indian Rupees [US$37.41  million]
		of which 91%
		was Temperature Controlled Services).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	Dragon Crown Group Holdings Limited reported sales of 214.22 million Chinese Renmimbi (US$31.84 million)
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
			a
			
			decrease of 1.9%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 218.29 million Chinese Renmimbi.
	
		The sales level in 2016 was fairly close to the level five years ago: in 2011, Dragon Crown Group Holdings Limited had sales
		of 199.44 million Chinese Renmimbi.
	

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










