 Career History



Founder

                                    Tenure Unconfirmed                


Dragon Crown Group Holdings Ltd.


                  Dragon Crown Group Holdings Ltd. engages in the provision of terminal and storage of liquid chemical services from loading and discharging of liquid chemical products. Its activities involve in the operation of terminals in Nanjing, Tianjin, and Ningbo. The company was founded on July 16, 2010 and is headquartered in Hong Kong.                




President

                                    2004 - 2007                


Nanjing Dragon Crown Liquid Chemical Terminal Co., Ltd.






Chairman & General Manager

                                    1997 - 2006                


Ningbo Free Trade Zone Dragon Crown Chemical Intl Co., Ltd.






Founder

                                    Prior                


Dragon Source Industrial Ltd.







