Dragon Crown Group Holdings Ltd.

                    Dragon Crown Group Holdings Ltd. engages in the provision of terminal and storage of liquid chemical services from loading and discharging of liquid chemical products. Its activities involve in the operation of terminals in Nanjing, Tianjin, and Ningbo. The company was founded on July 16, 2010 and is headquartered in Hong Kong.                  




Non-Executive Director

                    2004 - 2009                  


Future World Financial Holdings Ltd.

                    Future World Financial Holdings Ltd. is an investment holding company, which engages in the trading of health and consumer products. It operates through the following segments: Trading Business and Related Services, Securities Trading and Investment, Provision of Financing Services, Property Investment, and Licensing of e-Commerce Platform. The company was founded on October 21, 2002 and headquartered in Hong Kong.                  




